{"tid":2095812,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"史上最安靜毒品趴 警驚見10名瘖啞人無聲搖咧搖","createTime":"2020-07-05T18:14:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T22:38:20.000Z","uid":263991,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"10c1115369abcd9525bc1e3a38032a45da35dffd","tid":2095812,"uid":263991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T18:14:38.000Z","msg":"新北警林口分局3日晚間獲得線報，埋伏跟監一名姜姓毒品通緝犯時，發現他藏匿在板橋<br />\n光華街一處民宅，於是派員前往查緝，但在住處勘查時，卻發現屋內一片「靜悄悄」，<br />\n破門而入後，驚見姜嫌與另外10名男子在現場搖頭晃腦開毒趴，但離奇的是現場卻沒音<br />\n樂，卻滿桌毒品，事後才發現原來現場全是瘖啞人士，員警這時才恍然大悟，戲稱這是<br />\n查獲過史上最安靜的毒趴。<br />\n<br />\n警方在3日晚間接獲線報在板橋區有毒品通緝犯姜嫌窩藏，並販賣毒品安非他命供喑啞人<br />\n士吸食，遂前往查緝。經現地查訪且與屋主聯絡確定後，由屋主開門進入屋內，發現姜<br />\n嫌與10名喑啞人正在客廳開毒趴為其中一人慶生，警方在桌上發現毒品安非他命2袋（0<br />\n.21g、0.42g)、吸食器及海洛因香菸，遂將在場11名犯嫌依據毒品危害防制條例移送新<br />\n北地檢偵辦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由於警方無法調動多輛車載運這群開毒趴的瘖啞人士，熱心的國光客運為感謝泰山分駐<br />\n所為新北市治安的努力，便主動提出願意派車協助派出所將嫌犯移送至林口警分局集中<br />\n管理。<br />\n<br />\n林口警分局呼籲，一旦上了癮，吸毒者要面對的不止是身體的損害，最可怕的莫過於既<br />\n痛苦又冗長的戒毒過程，請勿以身試法！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/amp/realtimenews/20200704003442-260402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Famp%2Frealtimenews%2F20200704003442-260402&d=yjoviXv3QiMsqLwchXvj367%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=8f33e6be\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/amp/realtimenews/20200704003442-260402</a>"},{"pid":"184a41e60a8b148c47b369166c7268b38f51470c","tid":2095812,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T18:19:28.000Z","msg":"食煙合法<br />\n吸毒犯法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"143fb181e7332a5f9c50606da2972cacd6fb820a","tid":2095812,"uid":271851,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T18:22:16.000Z","msg":"🤚👈🤟👇👇👉🤚🤛🤏🤘👎👍👌☝️👆"},{"pid":"fefe91d532d6b135c6650b3684721410c149fbf0","tid":2095812,"uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T18:23:38.000Z","msg":"依家唔係事必要你講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d785b10c0fb7c5b382c8b5759ff9ea441c20178","tid":2095812,"uid":277551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T18:26:48.000Z","msg":"Brooklyn99 第2季咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ce67b0c99aee3504c81dacf0a29bbbb487290b","tid":2095812,"uid":203431,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T18:31:22.000Z","msg":"一路做手語一路Fing？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e95ba27e24ee5cf19340d0e117c610b5e134684b","tid":2095812,"uid":239205,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"15ce67b0c99aee3504c81dacf0a29bbbb487290b","tid":2095812,"uid":203431,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T18:31:22.000Z","msg":"一路做手語一路Fing？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T18:40:26.000Z","msg":"搞到我諗起d地獄meme圖 手語嘈交好似卡卡西咁勁快結手印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"379a9b07112b4e01b1643db3204dbaf0b7a55b3c","tid":2095812,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T18:49:29.000Z","msg":"十名男子開party<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?無女？"},{"pid":"042b2d62b7f02b007f8b1cb94d556017a7fd9cc5","tid":2095812,"uid":191338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T19:18:48.000Z","msg":"好有畫面，唔知聾啞人士幻覺會唔會聽到聲講到野"},{"pid":"b993cfd6166e85bc860afb653616b2267741afde","tid":2095812,"uid":106739,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T